  "content": "<!-- wp:group {\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Hero: Simple\"},\"align\":\"full\",\"backgroundColor\":\"surface\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|section-large\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|section-large\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"760px\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-surface-background-color has-background\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--section-large);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--section-large)\">\n\t<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1,\"fontSize\":\"heading-1\"} -->\n\t<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading has-heading-1-font-size\">Commercial HVAC maintenance that prevents downtime</h1>\n\t<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\t<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n\t<p class=\"has-large-font-size\">Scheduled service and fast emergency repair for facilities teams that cannot afford a failed system.</p>\n\t<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\t<!-- wp:buttons -->\n\t<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n\t\t<!-- wp:button -->\n\t\t<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"/contact\">Request a quote</a></div>\n\t\t<!-- /wp:button -->\n\t\t<!-- wp:button {\"className\":\"is-style-outline\"} -->\n\t\t<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"tel:+15550100143\">Call (555) 010-0143</a></div>\n\t\t<!-- /wp:button -->\n\t</div>\n\t<!-- /wp:buttons -->\n\t<!-- wp:image {\"width\":\"1600px\",\"height\":\"900px\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"style\":{\"border\":{\"radius\":\"var(--wp--custom--radius--medium)\"}}} -->\n\t<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized has-custom-border\"><img src=\"https://placehold.co/1600x900/1f6feb/ffffff?text=HVAC+Service\" alt=\"Technician servicing a rooftop HVAC unit\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" style=\"border-radius:var(--wp--custom--radius--medium)\"/></figure>\n\t<!-- /wp:image -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Section: Page Intro\"},\"align\":\"full\",\"backgroundColor\":\"base\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|section-medium\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|section-medium\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"760px\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-base-background-color has-background\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--section-medium);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--section-medium)\">\n\t<!-- wp:heading {\"fontSize\":\"heading-2\"} -->\n\t<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-heading-2-font-size\">Built for facilities that run on uptime</h2>\n\t<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\t<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n\t<p>If a rooftop unit fails, you need a partner who already knows your equipment. We pair scheduled maintenance with <a href=\"/services/emergency-hvac\">emergency repair service</a> so small issues never become shutdowns.</p>\n\t<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Section: Text + Image\"},\"align\":\"full\",\"backgroundColor\":\"surface\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|section-medium\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|section-medium\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-surface-background-color has-background\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--section-medium);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--section-medium)\">\n\t<!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|xl\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|xl\"}}}} -->\n\t<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center\">\n\t\t<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n\t\t<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\">\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:heading {\"fontSize\":\"heading-2\"} -->\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-heading-2-font-size\">A plan that adapts to your equipment</h2>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n\t\t\t<p>We document every unit on your site, set a service cadence that matches its load, and flag parts before they fail. You get one schedule, one contact, and no surprises.</p>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:buttons -->\n\t\t\t<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n\t\t\t\t<!-- wp:button {\"className\":\"is-style-outline\"} -->\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"/services/maintenance-plans\">See all maintenance plans</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- /wp:button -->\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:buttons -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- /wp:column -->\n\t\t<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n\t\t<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\">\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:image {\"width\":\"800px\",\"height\":\"600px\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"style\":{\"border\":{\"radius\":\"var(--wp--custom--radius--medium)\"}}} -->\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized has-custom-border\"><img src=\"https://placehold.co/800x600/f7f8fa/4b5563?text=On-site+Visit\" alt=\"Field technician inspecting an air handler\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" style=\"border-radius:var(--wp--custom--radius--medium)\"/></figure>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:image -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- /wp:column -->\n\t</div>\n\t<!-- /wp:columns -->\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Section: Process Steps\"},\"align\":\"full\",\"backgroundColor\":\"base\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|section-medium\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|section-medium\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-base-background-color has-background\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--section-medium);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--section-medium)\">\n\t<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"fontSize\":\"heading-2\"} -->\n\t<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-heading-2-font-size\">Three steps to a serviced system</h2>\n\t<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\t<!-- wp:columns {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|m\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|m\"}}}} -->\n\t<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n\t\t<!-- wp:column -->\n\t\t<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"accent\",\"fontSize\":\"heading-3\"} -->\n\t\t\t<p class=\"has-accent-color has-text-color has-heading-3-font-size\"><strong>01</strong></p>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Book an assessment</h3>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n\t\t\t<p>We inventory your equipment and review service history on site.</p>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- /wp:column -->\n\t\t<!-- wp:column -->\n\t\t<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"accent\",\"fontSize\":\"heading-3\"} -->\n\t\t\t<p class=\"has-accent-color has-text-color has-heading-3-font-size\"><strong>02</strong></p>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Get a cadence</h3>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n\t\t\t<p>We propose a service schedule and a flat monthly plan for your sign-off.</p>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- /wp:column -->\n\t\t<!-- wp:column -->\n\t\t<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"accent\",\"fontSize\":\"heading-3\"} -->\n\t\t\t<p class=\"has-accent-color has-text-color has-heading-3-font-size\"><strong>03</strong></p>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Stay ahead</h3>\n\t\t\t<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\t\t\t<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n\t\t\t<p>We service on schedule, log every visit, and respond fast when you call.</p>\n\t\t\